---
title: Resume Analysis Pipeline
---
flowchart LR
    A[📄 Raw Resume<br/>Text] --> B[🔧 parse_resume<br/>Extract structure]
    B --> C[📊 Parsed Data<br/>Skills, Experience,<br/>Education]
    C --> D[🔧 analyze_skills<br/>Gap analysis vs<br/>target role]
    C --> E[🔧 score_ats<br/>ATS compatibility<br/>check]
    D --> F[📋 Gap Report<br/>Missing skills,<br/>Transferable skills]
    E --> G[📋 ATS Score<br/>Keyword match,<br/>Format issues]
    F --> H[🔧 suggest_improvements<br/>Actionable rewrites]
    G --> H
    H --> I[✅ Final Report<br/>Score + Recommendations]

    style A fill:#95a5a6,color:#fff
    style I fill:#27ae60,color:#fff
